### Configuration File Deep Dive

The `tailwind.config.js` file controls every aspect of your Tailwind setup:

```js
/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
module.exports = {
  content: ['./src/**/*.{html,js}'],
  theme: {
    extend: {
      // custom additions
    },
  },
  plugins: [],
}
```

### theme.extend vs theme

- **theme** - Completely replaces the default theme
- **theme.extend** - Merges your values on top of the defaults (recommended)

```js
// Extend (adds to defaults - recommended)
theme: {
  extend: {
    colors: {
      brand: '#3490dc',
    },
  },
}

// Override (replaces entire default theme)
theme: {
  colors: {
    brand: '#3490dc',
  },
}
```

### Custom Colors

```js
theme: {
  extend: {
    colors: {
      primary: {
        50: '#eff6ff',
        100: '#dbeafe',
        200: '#bfdbfe',
        500: '#3b82f6',
        600: '#2563eb',
        700: '#1d4ed8',
        800: '#1e40af',
        900: '#1e3a5f',
      },
    },
  },
}
```

Usage: `bg-primary-500`, `text-primary-700`

### Custom Spacing

```js
theme: {
  extend: {
    spacing: {
      '18': '4.5rem',
      '72': '18rem',
      '84': '21rem',
      '96': '24rem',
    },
  },
}
```

### Custom Fonts

```js
theme: {
  extend: {
    fontFamily: {
      display: ['Inter', 'sans-serif'],
      body: ['Merriweather', 'serif'],
    },
  },
}
```

Usage: `font-display`, `font-body`

### Custom Breakpoints

```js
theme: {
  extend: {
    screens: {
      'xs': '475px',
      '3xl': '1600px',
    },
  },
}
```

### @apply Directive

Use `@apply` to extract repeated utility patterns into custom classes in your CSS:

```css
.btn-primary {
  @apply bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded
         hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors;
}
```

### Config Presets

Share configuration across projects:

```js
module.exports = {
  presets: [
    require('@acme/tailwind-preset'),
  ],
  theme: {
    extend: {
      // project-specific overrides
    },
  },
}
```

codeExample:
/* tailwind.config.js */
/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
module.exports = {
  content: ['./src/**/*.{html,js,jsx}'],
  darkMode: 'class',
  theme: {
    extend: {
      colors: {
        brand: {
          light: '#93c5fd',
          DEFAULT: '#3b82f6',
          dark: '#1e40af',
        },
      },
      fontFamily: {
        heading: ['Poppins', 'sans-serif'],
      },
      spacing: {
        '128': '32rem',
      },
      animation: {
        'fade-in': 'fadeIn 0.5s ease-in-out',
      },
      keyframes: {
        fadeIn: {
          '0%': { opacity: '0' },
          '100%': { opacity: '1' },
        },
      },
    },
  },
  plugins: [],
}
